Function.Description: The debugBrowsableProcs function returns a string of the currently active Analytic Information Server Lambdas in the context.

Brief.Overview: The debugBrowsableProcs function returns a string of the currently active Analytic Information Server Lambdas in the context. Locked Analytic Information Server Lambdas are not included. There are no arguments.
Brief.Usage: The debugBrowsableProcs function is used to get a list of the currently active Lambdas.

Syntax.Return: A string containing the names of the currently active Lambdas and the corresponding object id of the Lambda.
